  "1898880": {
    "name": "The Silent Swan",
    "steam_appid": 1898880,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898880/extras/654d703af95f2ee31aef1121fb44a9d9.avif?t=1720578563\" width=616 height=160 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><br>故事发生在 Mirov Kavrazyma 进入墙外土地追捕 Selene 的过程中，他的妻子也是堕落的唯一见证人，她消失得无影无踪——除了一系列四翼纸天鹅。这些天鹅包含她留下的文字，似乎是为了被米罗夫发现和追踪。<br><br>在整个游戏过程中，米罗夫将逐渐接近发生在他家的灾难（也称为坠落）的床边，并接近他决心挖掘的真相，同时一种奇怪的不安警告他最好走回去。<br><br>《寂静的天鹅》讲述了两个城市的故事：乌尔朱姆和塞尔努尔；两个冲突：过去和未来；和两个人；塞勒涅和米罗夫。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898880/extras/b3eacdd00b12c2da8687ed9a91afdac4.poster.avif?t=1720578563\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898880/extras/b3eacdd00b12c2da8687ed9a91afdac4.webm?t=1720578563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898880/extras/b3eacdd00b12c2da8687ed9a91afdac4.mp4?t=1720578563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898880/extras/cbaf1f4d42d7139cd8b80a65733f0efe.avif?t=1720578563\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898880/extras/bd23ec7fe88957269b585e7ce5ec13b6.avif?t=1720578563\" width=616 height=160 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><br>游戏玩法方面，《寂静的天鹅》遵循探索和收集物品的开放世界公式，但带有叙事曲折，成为那些在废弃土地上行走的人的信件和故事，以及这些相同的信件作为指南和进一步获取更多故事的工具。<br><br>由墙壁定义的巨大的世界对他们来说是稀疏的城市区域。这些城市区域都由陆桥连接——地面上的陆桥——玩家可以骑自行车导航。<br><br>这些楼层本身就是整体的城市区域，其特点是每栋建筑、每一层、每条人行道都可以完全穿越。这将服务于纯粹的环境和艺术目的，以及迫使玩家阅读引导前进方向的字母和对话的工具。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898880/extras/0ca28101b1e9d1d435e5458bfa4b149c.poster.avif?t=1720578563\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898880/extras/0ca28101b1e9d1d435e5458bfa4b149c.webm?t=1720578563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898880/extras/0ca28101b1e9d1d435e5458bfa4b149c.mp4?t=1720578563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898880/extras/cbaf1f4d42d7139cd8b80a65733f0efe.avif?t=1720578563\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898880/extras/122d5ce8c2ba1e12135b257b69025ddd.avif?t=1720578563\" width=616 height=160 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>穿越令人惊叹的荒凉景观 - 伟大的城市和建筑从薄雾中升起，撕裂天空中前所未见的景观。<br></li><li>引人入胜的故事 - 追寻神秘的纸天鹅，它们掌握着 Land Beyond the Walls 的秘密和我们主人公的生活。<br></li><li> 开放世界的叙事转折——观察你的周围，让风景引导你穿越广阔的、完全可穿越的地形，在那里你将有字母和叙事线索来追踪探索。<br></li><li>多重结局 - 做出的决定将决定你的故事和你在途中遇到的角色的结局。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898880/extras/ee89f23c2fce9635a3da525eb1f68f4a.poster.avif?t=1720578563\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898880/extras/ee89f23c2fce9635a3da525eb1f68f4a.webm?t=1720578563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898880/extras/ee89f23c2fce9635a3da525eb1f68f4a.mp4?t=1720578563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
